      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Can\u0027t Stomach the Thought",
        "Client": "Unflappable Biologist",
        "Description": "During a survey of the Frost Islands,\r\nI was attacked by a Tetranadon\r\nand found myself inside its gut!\r\nI managed to escape, but others\r\nmight not be so lucky. Please\r\nhunt it before someone gets eaten!",
