        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Pris aux tripes",
        "Client": "Biologiste imperturbable",
        "Description": "Lors d\u0027une de mes exp\u00E9ditions\r\ndans l\u0027Archipel de glace, j\u0027ai\r\neu le malheur de finir dans\r\nla panse d\u0027un Tetranadon.\r\nJ\u0027ai r\u00E9ussi \u00E0 m\u0027enfuir, mais\r\nj\u0027ai eu du bol. Chasse-le\r\navant qu\u0027il dig\u00E8re quelqu\u0027un !",
